All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AccountGUI
A graphical user interface for managing user profiles in the application.
App
 
BaseGUI
The BaseGUI class represents the base structure for GUI pages in the streaming service.
BrowseMoviesPage
The BrowseMoviesPage class represents the GUI for browsing and searching movies.
DatabaseConnection
This class will connect to the db.
Film
This class represents a film with attributes such as title, description, release year, and genre.
FilmDAO
Data Access Object for handling film import database operations.
FilmHandler
Interface defining the core film data operations.
FilmImportGUI
A graphical user interface for importing films from CSV files.
FilmImportService
Service class responsible for coordinating the import of films from CSV files into the database.
FilmManager
The FilmManager class manages film data retrieval from the database and updates the GUI.
FilmViewHandler
Interface defining GUI update operations for film display.
HomePageGUI
The HomePageGUI class represents the main window of the streaming service.
ImportResult
Represents the result of a film import operation.
ImportSummaryDialog
A dialog window that displays a summary of film import results.
LoginPage
Represents the login page for the Media Streaming Service.
MoviePlayerUI
The MoviePlayerUI serves as a bare bones representation for how playing movies through the application might look like.
PasswordHasher
The PasswordHasher class provides functionality to hash plain-text passwords using the MD5 hashing algorithm.
ProfileHandler
Interface defining the operations for managing user profiles.
ProfileManager
The ProfileManager class manages user profiles, including saving and loading profiles via serialization, as well as handling profile selection, deletion, and viewing history.
ProfilePanel
The ProfilePanel class represents a GUI component for creating or managing a user profile.
Review
 
ReviewGUI
The ReviewGUI class represents a graphical user interface for rating movies.
ReviewHandler
Interface for handling film reviews in the media streaming service.
ReviewManager
This class creates and manages a file to store film reviews.
Session
This class will store the user that is currently logged in.
User
The User class represents a user in the media streaming service application.
UserAuthenticator
The UserAuthenticator class manages user authentication, registration, and profile loading operations.
UserDAO
The UserDAO class provides methods for performing database operations related to user data, including inserting and retrieving user records in the `staff` table.
UserProfile
Represents a user profile with a name and type (e.g., ADULT, CHILD).
UserProfile.ProfileType
Enum representing the type of user profile, which can be either ADULT or CHILD.
